                       "message":  "MENU-SHORTCUT-DISPLAY: reword stale \"same tests\" note in menu_tests doc\n\nCodex review (NEEDS_CORRECTION): the menu_tests.rs module doc still claimed the\nextracted file is \"behaviour-identical / same tests\", but this PR widened those\ntests (accelerator-display columns on the four equality tests + a focused\naccelerator test + widened round-trip destructures). Reworded to preserve the\nhistorical EGUIHOST-TEST-EXTRACTION note (originally a verbatim, behaviour-\nidentical move) while recording that MENU-SHORTCUT-DISPLAY subsequently widened\nthe tests. Doc-comment only; no code change.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context) \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e",
